{"tid":2496935,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"音樂教師疑安排學生參加假鋼琴考試 9年間涉詐騙逾10人共8.8萬元 被控11項欺詐罪","createTime":"2021-04-20T07:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T07:19:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dfcd9258e6341d10562b3aac542b043d71de7bac","tid":2496935,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"被告龔慧雯，被控11項欺詐罪，詳情指她虛假地向事主表示，會安排他們參英國皇家音樂學院聯合委員會的鋼琴級試、樂理試及演奏級文憑試等，以欺騙每場考試所需費用，而令自己獲益。在控罪中，有學生被騙1次，亦有人持續被騙3至4年，有一個學生由2010年至2018年均由被告代報考試，包括兩次二級鋼琴、兩次四級鋼琴、五級樂理、六級鋼琴、八級鋼琴及鋼琴演奏級文憑考試。<br />\n<br />\n據知被告曾任真光女子中學音樂教師，校長於2018年接獲家長的電話，查問鋼琴考試情況，但該校並非試場。其後經考評局及皇家音樂學院調查，揭發被告多年來隱藏的懷疑騙案，被告涉由報名、考試至發出證書均作假。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/BDF3KU7ZCBBY5EB6A5G4545CZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FBDF3KU7ZCBBY5EB6A5G4545CZY%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuJX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=7487f964\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FBDF3KU7ZCBBY5EB6A5G4545CZY%2F&h=4c0adeeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/BDF3KU7ZCBBY5EB6A5G4545CZY/</a>"},{"pid":"c3e0b9a71e41cce58e31767c97276e8873608168","tid":2496935,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31ce588aba6b715df76c045c6bdbdabd54ca3a7","tid":2496935,"uid":348454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"教畜咁撚高人工都要犯法、呃學生錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b42df7cdf8713e1b9a879b00c9b58f3ea1f33a","tid":2496935,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31ce588aba6b715df76c045c6bdbdabd54ca3a7","tid":2496935,"uid":3484